---
title: Red Pesto Baked Chicken with Panzanella-Style Salad & Garlic Aioli
description: Our flavourful red pesto transforms this fuss-free meal into an Italian feast. We've paired it with tender chicken and included a hearty salad and garlicky croutons to make a hearty dinner the whole family will love.
